OL,6,FSpeaking on Sunday With Laura
OL,7,FKuenssberg, Culture Secretary Lisa
OL,8,FNandy said the security services like
OL,9,FMi5 and Mi6 will not be exempt from
OL,10,Fthe proposed bill.
OL,12,FThe security services will not be
OL,13,F"exempt" from the Hillsborough Law,
OL,14,Fthe Culture Secretary has said amid
OL,15,Ffears from campaigners and backbench
OL,16,FLabour MPs that the duty of candour is
OL,17,Fbeing watered down.
