OL,6,FThe mayors of Liverpool and Manchester
OL,7,Fhave called on the Government to
OL,8,Fwithdraw an amendment to the
OL,9,FHillsborough Law that "creates too
OL,10,Fbroad an opt-out" for the security
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FLiverpool City Region mayor Steve
OL,14,FRotheram and Greater Manchester mayor
OL,15,FAndy Burnham said on Saturday that the
OL,16,Famendment "risks undermining the
OL,17,Fspirit of the legislation".
