OL,6,FAmendments proposed by the Government
OL,7,Fon Wednesday brought spies within the
OL,8,Fscope of the legislation, subject to
OL,9,Fthe approval of the head of their
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,FHowever, campaigners have argued this
OL,13,Fwould allow those running the security
OL,14,Fservices to decide whether to disclose
OL,15,Finformation.
OL,17,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy said the
OL,18,F"challenge is to make sure that this
OL,19,Fapplies to the security services
OL,20,Fwithout fear or favour" and that they
OL,21,Fcan "continue to do their jobs".
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@WO]}D@EOU}D@_O]
