OL,6,FMs Nandy told the BBC's Sunday With
OL,7,FLaura Kuenssberg: "I just want to be
OL,8,Freally clear, the security services
OL,9,Fwon't be exempt."
OL,11,FShe added that it was important to
OL,12,F"never ever end up in a situation like
OL,13,Fwe did with the Manchester Arena
OL,14,Finquiry" where "security services are
OL,15,Fable to withhold information and
OL,16,Fpresent an inaccurate picture to
OL,17,Ffamilies and to a public inquiry for a
OL,18,Fvery long time".
