OL,6,FSome campaigners have warned that a
OL,7,Fdraft version of the legislation `
OL,8,Fformally known as the Public Office
OL,9,F(Accountability) Bill ` might allow
OL,10,Fintelligence chiefs to "hide serious
OL,11,Ffailures behind a vague claim of
OL,12,Fnational security".
OL,14,FThe Wigan MP rejected a suggestion
OL,15,Fthat the plans could be withdrawn amid
OL,16,Fthe threat of backbench opposition to
OL,17,Fit and said the Government is talking
OL,18,Fto families and campaigners.
