OL,6,FMPs had been due to debate the
OL,7,FHillsborough Law this week but the
OL,8,Fdiscussion was pushed back until
OL,9,FMonday to allow the Government to
OL,10,Fpropose changes that might address
OL,11,Fcampaigners' concerns.
OL,13,FMs Nandy added: "I'm confident that
OL,14,Fwe're going to resolve it. How it
OL,15,Fplays out tomorrow at the moment, is
OL,16,Fdependent on those conversations that
OL,17,Fwe have, but those conversations are
OL,18,Fgoing on right now."
