OL,6,FLabour Mayor of West Yorkshire Tracy
OL,7,FBrabin said that duty of candour
OL,8,Fregarding the security services was
OL,9,F"vital" for families who have
OL,10,Fcampaigned for the Hillsborough Law.
OL,12,FMs Brabin told the programme that the
OL,13,Flegislation was "95% there" but
OL,14,F"without the trust and confidence of
OL,15,Fthe families it's going to be very
OL,16,Fdifficult".
