OL,4,Cfrom Hillsborough Law'
OL,6,FThe Labour mayor said: "I think the
OL,7,Fduty of candour is so vital for the
OL,8,Fjustice for these families that have
OL,9,Fbeen fighting for decades. You can do
OL,10,Fit privately with a judge. There are
OL,11,Fways to do it."
OL,13,FMs Brabin added: "This government has
OL,14,Fshown an appetite to slow things down,
OL,15,Fto get things right.
OL,17,F"And I think this is a historic
OL,18,Flandmark piece of legislation, it's
OL,19,Freally worth leaning in to get it
OL,20,Fright."
